data.description: Welcome to your private oasis of luxury living perched on a large corner lot with picturesque views. This stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bath home is full of custom features throughout.  The gourmet kitchen with its 8'x12' butlers pantry will delight any home chef. The expansive primary suite is conveniently located on the main floor and features cozy fireplace, spa like ensuite bathroom and the closet of your dreams. The 2nd floor features 2 additional bedrooms, large bonus room and full bathroom. The crowning jewel of this property is the indoor/outdoor living with its 810sf sunroom that includes an outdoor kitchen. Beyond the sunroom is your backyard retreat with a sparkling in-ground 12'x24' heated pool, ample green space and built-in fireplace.
